  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You may use this skill if your subclass is Tracker, Spy, or Detective.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>Change 1 [Boss] or [Raid] enemy (selected by the GM) that is to appear in the next scene to the [Identified] state and obtain information on the target. If there is no corresponding enemy, the use of the skill will have failed, but will not count towards the use limit. </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>(Fumble): The enemy notices your scouting.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>A special skill that allows you to sense the presence of a powerful enemy and research that enemy before a confrontation. No enemy can escape your eyes.</p>",
